                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>
                       Miniatures added in the late 20th century by the "Speckled Garment Artist". ‎
                       Decorative designs, many folios employ line of alternating red and black dots as section ‎divider. ‎
                       </summary>
                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d01">
                           <locus target="#4r"></locus>
                           <desc>A miniature of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1025NativityJesus"></ref> with captions (left to right) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቅዱስ፡ ዮሴፍ, ሊደተ፡ ክርስቶስ, and ቅድስት፡ ሳሎሜ</foreign>
                           </desc>
                         </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d02">
                           <locus target = "#36r"></locus>
                           <desc>A miniature of the Annunciation with captions (left to right) <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል, እግዚእትነ፡ ማርያም፡, ብስራት, መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</foreign>
                           </desc>
                         </decoNote>
                         <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d03">
                               <locus target = "#55r"></locus>
                               <desc>A miniature of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild"></ref>
                               </desc>
                             </decoNote>
                         <decoNote type = "miniature" xml:id="d04">
                               <locus target = "#84v"></locus>
                               <desc>A miniature of the Baptism of Christ with captions (left to right) <foreign xml:lang = "gez">እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡, ከመ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አጥመቀ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ, እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ, ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡, ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡</foreign>
                               </desc>
                             </decoNote>
                         <decoNote type = "miniature" xml:id="d05">
                               <locus target = "#111v"></locus>
                               <desc>A miniature of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1024MosesLaw"></ref> with captions (left to right) <foreign xml:lang = "gez">እኁ፡ አሮን፡, ቅዱስ፡ ሙሴ፡, ጽለተ፡ ሙሴ, እኅቱ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>
                               </desc>
                             </decoNote>
                         <decoNote type ="miniature" xml:id="d06">
                               <locus target = "#147v"></locus>
                               <desc>A miniature of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1066DavidHarp"></ref> with captions (left to right) <foreign xml:lang = "gez">መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡, ቅዱስ፡ ዳዊት, </foreign>How David praised God with the harp, David playing the harp
                               </desc>
                             </decoNote>
                         <decoNote type = "miniature" xml:id="d07">
                               <locus target = "#163v"></locus>
                               <desc>A miniature of Mary and <persName ref = "PRS6820MaryMag"/> <ref type = "authFile" corresp = "AT1099StMary"/>
                               </desc>
                             </decoNote>

